accessibility.text: Figure Displays pencil functionalities on live caregiver stream
It allows for in app drawing, such as panning, zooming, highlighting on the fly, writing text, so that the caregiver and the other nurse/doc can both exchange a faster smoother communication.
Here we see what the other side of the communication channel may be looking at and may type for instructions to promptly give advice.
In case of low connectivity it is also possible to downscale the quality of video with lossy compression and/or interrupt whilst continuing recording and sending as media attachment for later use
